{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回 啸雨挥风掌如龙矣 行云流水步亦灵哉\n\n向衡飞于京城疏林中等候王一萍，两人首次见面即生惺惺相惜之感。王一萍出身书香世家，为南灵龙灵飞传人；向衡飞则久困穷域，乃威震河朔魏灵飞之徒。双方各怀师命，约定以十年之约决一胜负。短暂交手后，王一萍化解了与更夫的尴尬局面，邀请向衡飞到府中暂住数日再定胜负。二人在王宅后园发现一名夜行人，追踪而出后发现是江南桐庐的\"抱石书生\"贺衔山，因爱石成癖深夜入室寻石。王一萍欣然结交这位雅人，向衡飞虽心存疑虑却未多言。本章展示了两位主角性格的巨大反差：王一萍潇洒随意、轻裘肥马；向衡飞沉稳谨慎、重情重义，却在师命与友谊间陷入两难。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "阁下可是威震河朔魏大侠的传人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "兄台想必是龙大侠的传人了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "在下向衡飞，奉先师之命，在此恭候阁下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "小弟王一萍。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "听阁下的口音，也像是久居京城的，小弟终日在京城走动，却无缘得见阁下一面，真是可惜得很。",
      "tone": "惋惜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "先师与令师龙大侠，昔年曾有十年之约，故遗命小弟在此恭候兄台，方才小弟看到兄台入林时的身法，想必已尽得令师真传，小弟与兄台虽然一见如故，但却不敢忘却先师遗命，故不自量力，想领教领教兄台的绝艺。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "好，好，小弟虽然不才，却也正是要来领教领教威震河朔传下来的绝艺的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "阁下如果心急，现在就动手吧。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "请吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "更夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁呀？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "更夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在干什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "更夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是王公子。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "更夫",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "小的们还以为有什么歹徒在这里闹事呢？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "更夫",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "想不到原来是公子爷在这儿——",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们大惊小怪干吗？",
      "tone": "不满",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不过和向公子出来活动一下而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还站在这里干吗？",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快敲你们的更鼓去吧。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快走，今天的事可不准说出去，知道了吗？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "向兄，人生之际遇，实最难测，你我若非遇见先师和魏大侠，今日也不致动武，有缘相见，结成知友亦未可知，可是现在——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "现在你我各衔师命，却是势必要分出高下不可，就是今日分不出，明日也要分出，甚至于像我俩恩师般纠缠数十年亦未可知——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "只是你我都受了师恩，师命怎可违背，何况他们两位老人家仙游之前，唯一念念不忘的，也只有此事呢。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "今日夜已太深，这两个更夫又来惹厌，反正你我恩师所订之约，并未限定今天解决。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "向兄何不先与小弟盘桓三两日，让小弟能多领些教益，月尾之前，再寻一日决个胜负，日后无论谁胜谁败，你我仍是好友。",
      "tone": "恳切",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "我恩师的遗命，只是要我两人决一胜负而已，却并未禁止我两人交友呀！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "这样也好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "那么今宵向兄且去弟处，抵足而眠，今夕虽非良夕，但你我却可剪烛夜话，岂非快事。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "只是三数日后若分不出胜负的话——",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "那自然要等事过再说了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "那里就是寒舍了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "王兄家里还有些什么精通武功的人吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "没有呀！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "只怕有什么梁上君子要光顾敝舍了。",
      "tone": "惊恐",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "不会，不会，据我所知，京城之内的小偷，没有一人有此人的身手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "王兄总该进去查看查看吧。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "是、是，向兄也一齐去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "看不到人呀！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "向兄，我们到前面去看看那厮有何举动。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "text": "向兄，此人到底在弄些什么玄虚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们把这人弄出去问个明白。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "钉住他！",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友夤夜追踪，不知有何见教呢？",
      "tone": "从容",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "朋友夜入敝舍，却又有何见教呢？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "小弟冒昧，不知道阁下就是园林主人，恕罪、恕罪。",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "恕罪倒可免了——",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "不过朋友半夜三更闯入别人园子里，却是为的什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "此事说来，实是荒唐。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "只是小弟看阁下不但是位高人，还是个雅人，对小弟此一荒唐之举，也许可以原谅的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "请说。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "小弟虽是个武夫，但自幼即有爱石之癖，只要有好石头，千方百计地都要去搜罗来。",
      "tone": "自豪",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "阁下日后如有暇，不妨到寒舍去，小弟身无长物，家里各色各样的石头，也不知有多少块了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "府上在哪里？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "敝舍在江南桐庐，此次北来，就为的想搜集些石头回去的，但小弟在京城人地生疏，而除了巨宅深园之外，哪里找得到稀有的石头？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "是以小弟不嫌唐突，竟做了梁上君子了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "阁下真可算是雅贼了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那两个更夫又来了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无妨。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "家父昔年也爱石成癖，不是小弟说狂话，寒舍园中的山石，无论哪一块都是家父昔年重金收购来的。",
      "tone": "自豪",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "阁下找到寒舍，倒还真找对地方了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又来干吗？",
      "tone": "不满",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "兄台大名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "小弟贺衔山，江湖朋友抬爱，却将小弟叫做抱石书生。",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "这倒真是名副其实了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "小弟王一萍，是个江湖上的无名小卒而已。",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "text": "小弟虽然无才，但兄台这种雅人，却是小弟最喜结交的，兄台如果愿意，不妨也到舍下盘桓几天，家父所藏的那些石头，也要待名家的鉴定呢。",
      "tone": "恳切",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "text": "固所愿也，不敢求耳。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今夜一夜，小弟交到两位知己，真叫小弟太高兴了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 355
    }
